scene.message:
Maki: It seems a St. Hermelin{nl}
student slipped in here{nl}
ahead of us!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Do these guys even feel{nl}
any guilt for what they've{nl}
done?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Was Kandori having them{nl}
build a machine that creates{nl}
Demons, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: This is starting to{nl}
get complicated, and I don't{nl}
like it...{waitkey}{clearbox}There's stuff even I get and{nl}
stuff I don't, y'know!{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Are you all friends{nl}
of that high schooler from{nl}
before?{waitkey}I'm sorry to say{wait_fr:32} that he...{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Dr. Nicolai meant{nl}
to stop Kandori, but...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
what could we possibly do?{waitkey}{ret}

Scientist: Demons appearing in{nl}
town — even we didn't foresee{nl}
it.{waitkey}But it's a fascinating turn{nl}
of events, is it not?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Don't you agree?{waitkey}{ret}
